Pre-Requrities
   SSH Clinet
   Control Nodes
   Managed Nodes
   Sudo Access

OS Platforms:
   Linux
   CentOs
   Debian
   Ubuntu
   MacOS

Control Nodes:
    Need to Configure Python
    Need to Configure Ansible Core 2.14 

Managed Nodes:
    Need to configure Python

    
Steps:
  1) Update System packages
      sudo yum install update 
  2) Check ansible repositery is enabled or not
      sudo amazon-linux-extras | grep ansible2
  3) It's present please go to next step else enable the repo
      sudo amazon-linux-extras install ansible2    
  4) Install the ansible core
      amazon-linux-extras install ansible2 -y
  5) To verfiy the installation please check below command
      ansible --version
